        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Bring creativity and precision to your baking with Beille versatile 12 piece cookie cutter set, featuring four classic shapes in three convenient sizes each. The set includes: three hearts, three stars, three circles and three flowers, each in small, medium, and large sizes, perfect for layering, decorating, or creating matching sets.<br/><br/>Use the cookie cutters for cookies, biscuits, fondant, pastries, or even fruit and sandwich cutouts; these cookie cutters or cookie molds make home baking fun for all ages! And, crafted from durable stainless steel, each cookie cutter slices cleanly through dough without sticking or warping, ensuring consistent shapes every time, while the nested design makes storage simple and space saving.<br/><br/>Whether you’re preparing sugar cookies for the holidays, shaping biscuits for brunch, or adding charm to fondant and pastries, these cookie cutters make it easy to craft beautiful, uniform designs each and every time. Happy baking!",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
